(1766, 2, '2013-10-27 11:20:32', '2013-10-27 11:20:32', '[tds-section background="#fff" textcolor="#000"]\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=20]\n[tds-columns]\n[tds-column half]<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1791" alt="mac-02" src="http://takemephoto.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/mac-022.png" width="448" height="572" />[/tds-column]\n[tds-column half last]\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=80]\n<h2>Build your own [tds-highlight bg="#009FE3" color="#FFFFFF"]MARKETPLACE[/tds-highlight]</h2>\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=20]\nThe Product Vendors extension for WooCommerce allows you to turn your store into a multi-vendor marketplace, such as ''Etsy'' or ''Creative Market''. You can assign existing products to vendors, or they can add and edit their own ones – they will have a dedicated page on the site where they will be able to list all of their products, but they will also show up in your normal shop pages so you can sell your own products alongside those of your vendors.\n\nTo make things even more useful, you have complete control over how much commission each vendor receives for a sale and you can even manually add new commissions and edit existing ones.\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 6em;"><span style="color: #575757;">[tds-icon name=icon-circle-arrow-down]</span></p>\n[/tds-column]\n[/tds-columns]\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=20]\n[/tds-section]\n\n[tds-section background="#C5EBF9" textcolor="#000"]\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=60]\n[tds-columns]\n[tds-column half]\n<h2>Create a [tds-highlight bg="#009FE3" color="#FFFFFF"]MEMBERSHIP[/tds-highlight] website!</h2>\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=20]\nWC Subscriptions makes it easy to create and manage products with recurring payments. Create a subscription product just like any other WooCommerce product, and you’re ready to start selling subscriptions.\n<h6>What can you sell with Subscriptions?</h6>\nProducts that require shipping, like magazines\nDownloadable products, like stockphots, Musics, videos\nVirtual products, like memberships\nServices, like business coaching\nMembership access to content in combination with the Groups extension\nSell any other physical, virtual or downloadable product/service you can imagine!\n\n[/tds-column]\n[tds-column half last]<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1778" alt="EX01" src="http://takemephoto.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/EX011.png" width="860" height="572" />[/tds-column]\n[/tds-columns]\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=40]\n[/tds-section]\n\n[tds-section background="#fff" textcolor="#000"]\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=20]\n[tds-columns]\n[tds-column half]<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1793" alt="mac-01" src="http://takemephoto.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/mac-012.png" width="448" height="572" />[/tds-column]\n[tds-column half last]\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=140]\n<h2>Build your [tds-highlight bg="#009FE3" color="#FFFFFF"]DONATION[/tds-highlight] website!</h2>\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=20]\nThe WooCommerce Name Your Price extension lets you be flexible in what price you are willing to accept for selected products.\n\nYou can use this extension to accept user-determined donations, gather pricing data or to take a new approach to selling products! So, what are you waiting for? Start building your donation website right now!\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=20]\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 6em;"><span style="color: #575757;">[tds-icon name=icon-circle-arrow-up]</span></p>\n [/tds-column]\n[/tds-columns]\n[tds-divider invisible thickness=10]\n[/tds-section]', 'More business models', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'more-business-models', '', '', '2013-10-27 11:20:32', '2013-10-27 11:20:32', '', 0, 'http://theme-dutch.com/presents/joop/?page_id=1766', 0, 'page', '', 0),
